Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 帐篷里怎么这么大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是岔路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走哪边才好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点 前面有黑暗的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾里奥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人待在这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很孤单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是天马的寄宿者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾名为纳美尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这死亡之月的支配者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要艾里奥斯受到这种折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你了解真正的黑暗有多深吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种生长在光中的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会懂我的感受的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是很久以前的故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮上有个充满光辉的国家 银色千年王国
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在女王倩尼迪的统治下 非常昌盛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 在那背面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一位女王住在一颗冷清的小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在黑暗中注视着月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是黑暗女王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗女王非常嫉妒月亮王国的繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是想着要让那个王国成为自己所有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而后她终于知道一种具有不可思议力量的宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有它的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就能取月球女王而代之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不只如此 甚至还能统治宇宙的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个宝石 就是黄金水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在地球的圣地 由一名少年守护着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗女王自己也不明白那种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个时候 黑暗女王想要的不再只是宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想连同那少年一块儿占为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“让我们一起用黄金水晶的力量统治世界吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她这么对少年说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“黄金水晶会自己选择主人”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“若你拥有美丽的梦想的话”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“就能获得这块宝石”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“可若不是这样…”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“若你心存不轨 就会受到惩罚”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那神圣火焰 黑暗女王没有拿到黄金水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而白色之月的女王还将她封印在了新月的阴影之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 黑暗女王抓住了机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要拥有黄金水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就能冲破结界的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 在期待已久的日蚀之时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她释放出了自己的族人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于成功抓住了那个少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾里奥斯没有伤害你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快点放了艾里奥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 可恨的白色之月一族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在该我复仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝我多年以来的怨愤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会任你称心如意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不原谅反抗我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉鲁科尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢陛下的体谅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那些个白色之月的人太碍眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我干掉她们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太令人失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉帕拉好想骑天马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候就不管我们 太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该反一把的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我们不能背叛纳美尼亚女王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观察天体的道具啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平时都有好好学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要报告纳美尼亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太会调整啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳美尼亚大人会把它认成本尊的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球球开门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好办啊 开了这么大个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我们抓到了黄金之镜的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换掉她的话就是坏搞破坏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们已经逃不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有美丽的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用我现在的黑暗力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样可以随心所欲地控制黄金水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然还包括你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么镜子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像镜子迷宫一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手月亮 该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着瞧吧 小女孩们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把那些小女孩们给我打到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 都在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手月亮?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走岔了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手木星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 你不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:12:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我就是你 真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要成为一个战士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的我应该更女性化才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插花 做点心 我梦想中的生活是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 没有人了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续战斗的话 我就越来越不像女孩儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实是这样一个女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我放弃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起做美梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天到晚做这种事真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想明明是想要成为一名医生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你已经放弃了那时的梦想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来 我明明这么辛苦的在守护和平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没有人会表扬我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那些忘恩负义的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为自己的梦想活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能一直都打败敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定这一次就会被打败
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想逃避啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想 逃 避…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很害怕吧 我都懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你的一切我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 跟我一起做美梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 忘记所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做一个很美的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手月亮 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心现在有多痛 难道你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所遭受的痛苦就是我的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候 我很自由 很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在我有了可以分享苦痛的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我对现在的自己非常满意 一点都不后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的人根本就不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现出你的真实身份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:29.77,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}Moon Tiara Action！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:37.72,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}金星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.13,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}爱与美的冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:49.08,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}水星 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:54.26,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}水之狂想曲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用这种法术来骗我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太小看水手战士们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会抛弃童年的梦想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 现在的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有着更大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 你们都不能活着离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要第一个上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 天马好像不是实体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在看什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢笑话我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可抓住了你的寄宿者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你不老实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家伙真是不听话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 球球编绳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你是天马 这样也跑不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后你就是我们的宠物了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个角 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说那是老太婆说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金水晶?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能拿得下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不喜欢你这种态度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉帕拉被烧伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要惩罚他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再紧一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你们对天马做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个火不是我们弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也顺便叫它把这些火给灭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被烤成马肉烧烤大会的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能看着他被烧焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跑进了火中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.67,0:20:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么能做到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我只是想救天马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丫头们！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你们做了什么好事 你们这群大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆 放我们出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳美尼亚女王大人 很快就会放我们出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉恩吉恩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那个叫小月亮的小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量明明不如我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是感觉好像是我们输了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:02.97,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦啦  绝不放弃  继续努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:06.97,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这场胜负全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:11.06,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期盼的热情加速了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:18.02,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在青春期的年纪 恋爱的轮廓总是不停的转变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.70,0:22:33.33,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后  我对一位偷心者一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:41.17,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他如同过往的情人  乱了我的情绪  不知是否会再度受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:48.22,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办？ 但我已经决定 想要故意捉弄他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:57.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飘扬于风中的水手服  我要坦荡荡地做自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:03.65,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦啦 绝不放弃  继续努力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:07.91,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:11.62,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张的悸动加速了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:18.75,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在青春期的年纪 恋爱的轮廓总是不停的转变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.44,0:23:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了解开这可恶封印的时刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.37,0:23:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金火焰将无法再灼伤我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你这么做的 黄金水晶是美丽梦想的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的梦想 就由我来守护
